## 📋 Requirements

### System
- ✅ Android 5.0+ (API 21+) — extensively tested on Android 14/15
- ✅ Root access (Magisk recommended)
- ✅ LSPosed Framework installed (even if the manager crashes, the framework itself works)
- ✅ BusyBox or ROM with complete binaries (sqlite3, awk, sed)

### Connectivity
- ✅ ADB enabled for remote installation
- ✅ Shell access (su) for local execution

### Compatibility
- ✅ Magisk 20.0+
- ✅ LSPosed v1.8.0+
- ✅ POSIX shell compatible

